// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4638 — Mass File Rename (safepay)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a3c69462-a50b-50fd-80ac-26a1db982384

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
